{"tid":2120771,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國藥武肺疫苗有望年底上市 董事長： 效果非常理想 冇嚴重副作用 有效性100%","createTime":"2020-07-23T01:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T08:27:31.000Z","uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"ad371def1d5080e748fbf2a6340ab5a1bc6e02e2","tid":2120771,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:44:26.000Z","msg":"國藥集團董事長劉敬楨表示，<del>新冠</del>武漢肺炎疫苗研究應該說已經成功，年底或可上市。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，<del>新冠</del>武漢肺炎疫苗是國藥集團旗下北京生物製品研究所和武漢生物製品研究所合作研發，而他在3月30日已經自先進行預注射，相當於「以身試藥」。4月12日，疫苗進入國內一二期臨床試驗，效果非常理想，無一例有嚴重的副反應，有效性可以說是100%。6月底，已獲批開始進行國際三期臨床試驗，年底或可上市。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，公司兩個所同時建了P3級別的生產設施，可以保證下一步疫苗大規模量產化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.finet.hk/newscenter/news_content/5f18b084bde0b33df4743df4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.finet.hk%2Fnewscenter%2Fnews_content%2F5f18b084bde0b33df4743df4&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgFSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=6b1415be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.finet.hk/newscenter/news_content/5f18b084bde0b33df4743df4</a>"},{"pid":"d5039952ff299e329bad6e68b53354c4fe218500","tid":2120771,"uid":18477,"like":110,"dislike":2,"score":108,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:49:31.000Z","msg":"點解會有效性100%？<br />\n因為你哋班objects整出嚟㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43e007032fc4ad9d6c193b6671a23fe2b983822","tid":2120771,"uid":342828,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:50:04.000Z","msg":"國藥集團董事長劉敬楨表示，新冠武漢肺炎疫苗研究<ins>應該說</ins>已經成功，年底<ins>或</ins>可上市。<br />\n<br />\n又要威，又要戴頭盔，仲要戴兩個㖭！"},{"pid":"56966d08dcfaaac62b9b1f179099c5003cc59ef4","tid":2120771,"uid":50386,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:51:09.000Z","msg":"冇副作用唔代表有效喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835cfcbd33c12708fb646efa8ae534c9c8e0a765","tid":2120771,"uid":214502,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:52:10.000Z","msg":"見到100%